Employee: Jane Morrison
Employee ID: EID-4721
Position: Senior Employee Relations Specialist
Review Period: January 1, 2024 – December 31, 2024
Manager: Mark Sullivan
Overall Rating: Exceeds Expectations (4.2 / 5.0)

Compensation Details
Base Salary: $112,000
Annual Bonus Awarded: 12% ($13,440)
Merit Increase: 4.5% (new base $117,040 effective 01/01/2025)
Equity Refresh: 200 RSUs, 4-year vesting schedule

Manager Feedback
Jane delivered exceptional conflict resolution outcomes, mediating 14 complex disputes with zero litigation escalations. She led the design and rollout of the Remote Work Conduct Policy, adopted across all U.S. locations with 94% employee satisfaction. During the Q3 reorganization, she personally coached 7 managers through difficult performance conversations, preventing 3 potential wrongful termination claims. Her proactive case documentation set a new standard adopted by the entire team. Opportunities: expand cross-functional collaboration with Legal to identify systemic compliance risks earlier in the policy drafting cycle.

