Employee: David Okonkwo
Employee ID: EID-2289
Position: Employee Relations Partner
Review Period: January 1, 2024 – December 31, 2024
Manager: Mark Sullivan
Overall Rating: Meets Expectations (3.5 / 5.0)

Compensation Details
Base Salary: $89,500
Annual Bonus Awarded: 8% ($7,160)
Merit Increase: 3.2% (new base $92,364 effective 01/01/2025)

Manager Feedback
David reliably managed his caseload of 37 employee concerns with thorough documentation and adherence to SLAs. He demonstrated solid investigation skills in two harassment complaints, both resolved within policy timelines. He provided critical support during the annual handbook review by updating key sections on leave policies. Development areas: improve stakeholder communication by providing more frequent status updates to business leaders; take ownership of at least one process improvement initiative in 2025. His work is consistent and accurate but lacks the strategic reach needed for the next level.

