Employee: Maria Gonzalez
Employee ID: EID-8315
Position: Employee Relations Coordinator
Review Period: January 1, 2024 – December 31, 2024
Manager: Jane Morrison
Overall Rating: Exceeds Expectations (4.5 / 5.0)

Compensation Details
Base Salary: $74,000
Annual Bonus Awarded: 10% ($7,400)
Merit Increase: 5.0% (new base $77,700 effective 01/01/2025)
Special Recognition Award: $2,500 (one-time)

Manager Feedback
Maria transformed the intake process by implementing a new digital triage system, reducing average response time from 2.3 days to 8 hours. She has become the team’s go‑to expert on FMLA and ADA interactive processes, training 22 HR business partners across the organization. Her data integrity work during the quarterly audit uncovered a $14,000 overpayment to a vendor, which was fully recovered. She is clearly ready for expanded responsibilities. Recommendation: promote to ER Partner within the next two review cycles.

